OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A father has started legal action      
OL,6, against UK oil giant BP over the death 
OL,7, of his 21-year-old son.                
OL,9,FHussein Julood alleges the burning off 
OL,10,Fof gas at a BP-run oil field in Iraq - 
OL,11,Fa practise known as flaring - caused   
OL,12,Fhis son Ali's leukaemia.               
OL,14,FA BBC investigation in 2022 found Ali's
OL,15,Fvillage, which lies within the field,  
OL,16,Fhad high levels of cancer-causing      
OL,17,Fpollutants known to come from flaring. 
OL,19,FBP said "we understand the concerns"   
OL,20,Fand are supporting change.             
